This directory contains all currently available slides. Note that we do not yet provide slides for the whole book. We will gradually add to the available slide deck over time.

You can either download the complete set of available slides (qrm.pdf), or you can download individual numbered chapter files (qrm_xx.pdf) although some hyperlinks across chapters will be broken in this case.

If you click on file names the PDF will display in the GitHub viewer. To download the file, click on the Raw button.
